Text: Turret Phone Outageat approximately PM there will be an Turret phone outage lasting until PM All phones will be inoperable during this period This outage is necessary to resynchronize all line and trader information i n the switch Night traders on the Power Desk will have Lucent phone oper ation during this period for the East Watts Line Thank you for your patience David A Cummings Office Cell
